      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " in his thoughts. But as the reading there is doubtful, both the Samaritan and the LXX. texts having ‘a stretched out arm’ instead of ‘a mighty hand,’ we cannot be confident that we have here a quotation.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
